    "final_verdict": "Leea Education Agent shows strong promise with a score of 7/10 overall. The project demonstrates innovative thinking in educational technology but requires more detailed technical specifications and implementation plans. Recommendations: 1) Develop clear metrics for measuring educational effectiveness, 2) Strengthen data privacy and security documentation, 3) Create detailed technical architecture diagrams, 4) Establish concrete testing procedures with education experts, 5) Define clear monetization strategy. The project should proceed with development while addressing these key areas."
